 this is a good topic to spend some time reviewing in detail with your potential advisor does your firm have a dedicated investments staff many firms have their principals also doing the investment strategy many firms have their principals also doing the investment strategy  at hb we have a dedicated investment staff focused solely on investments research every day not on serving clients  but we mix in the client perspective and the experience of our partners by having both groups on our investment committee that makes our investment decisions do you use a third party custodian this is a critical question that should always be asked most independent firms like homrich berg will use a third party custodian like charles schwab or fidelity this is a critical question that should always be asked  most independent firms like homrich berg will use a third party custodian like charles schwab or fidelity  this provides you as the client an independent way to verify your assets outside of reports from your advisor the client relationship can you show me a consolidated performance report for all my investments some firms will send you monthly or quarterly account balance information but not true total return performance data some firms will send you monthly or quarterly account balance information but not true total return performance data  other firms may give you an overall portfolio view but no details on how individual managers or funds are performing vs benchmarks or what is driving your overall performance  hb gives you online access to your entire portfolio at any time with updated values net of fees and expenses who will work with me how big will my client service team be at hb you will typically have  people on your client service team and the culture of our firm is for the entire firm to serve you as a client at hb you will typically have  people on your client service team and the culture of our firm is for the entire firm to serve you as a client  some firms with 